    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried walking and it didn't really help much, if anything i just feel more lightheaded. i really dont want to go to the hospital because the waits are so bad and it's expensive, and honestly i've had these exact same feelings during panic attacks before so i'm hoping it's just that again. do you think it's safe to just take some herbal calming tea or maybe a magnesium supplement and just sleep it off?",
