      "content": "Taking herbal calming tea and magnesium supplements can be a good way to relax and soothe your symptoms. Just be sure to choose high-quality, natural ingredients and avoid anything with caffeine or alcohol. Sleep is also important, so try to get enough rest. However, if your symptoms persist or worsen, it's always wise to consult a healthcare professional. Remember, it's important to listen to your body and take care of yourself. Stay safe and take care!",
      "source": "target",
